data.revised_prompt: Create a realistic and detailed image of a 'Chocolate Espresso Martini' cocktail. The drink is served in a traditional martini glass, presenting a rich, velvety brown shade. Soft crema is layered on top, adorned with three coffee beans placed strategically. The inclusion of chocolate syrup provides a delicate sheen under warm, atmospheric lighting, resulting in soft highlights and shadows. Light reflection gives the glossy surface an elegant look. The backdrop incorporates a dark wooden pattern, enhancing the luxurious appeal of the beverage. The image composition is balanced, accentuating the attractive cocktail texture and garnishes, situated in an enchanting, ambient setting. The martini is made up of 1 oz Vodka, 1 oz Coffee liquer, 1 oz freshly brewed espresso, and 0.5 oz chocolate syrup. The background should be clear with a soft focus, in a photorealistic style, imitating the standard of a professional food photographer. No text or watermarks should be included in the image.
